
    TWO men Nkosinathi 'Mazinyo' Ngwenya aged 28-years-old and Nkosinathi
Moyo 30-years-old received four life sentences and 100 years for murder.The two were sentenced for attempted murder, house robbery
and possession of unlicensed firearms.Cops arrested the accused in August 2016 after a community
member who was tired of crime in Zandspruit gave intelligence about the group
